character.name:
Skin Tone: Light-to-medium brown with warm undertones. 

Headwear: White turban, neatly wrapped, smooth fabric with clear folds, sitting high on the head, symmetrical wrap. 

Hair: Not visible due to turban. Face Shape: Rounded oval face with full cheeks and broad forehead. 

Eyebrows: Thick, dark eyebrows. 

Eyes: Dark eyes, warm and friendly appearance. 

Facial Hair: Full dark beard, large length, dense and well-groomed; mustache connected and neatly trimmed. 

Clothing: Black traditional kurta Buttoned placket at the chest Long sleeves Smooth fabric with minimal folds White shawl/scarf draped over one shoulder
